select 
    d.[DateNum],
    createdate(getyear(d.[Date]),d.[MonthNum],d.[DayNumOfMonth]) as Date,
    d.[MonthName],
    d.[DayName]
from [Dates] d

configOptions.importQuery:
SELECT 
    a._id,
    a.name,
    a.description,
    a.createdBy_id,
    a.createdBy_email,
    a.dateCreated,
    a.dateUpdated,
    a.dateLastUsed,
    a.enabled,
    wat.last_used,
    0 as left_join
FROM "prismWebDB"."webAccessTokenKeys" a
left join (
select 
    f.webAccessTokenId,
    max(f.[dateCreated]) as last_used
from webAccessTokenUsage f
group by f.[webAccessTokenId] 
) wat on wat.webAccessTokenId = a._id
